body: * Fix bug that push with no arg getting runtime exception: https://github.com/jingweno/gh/pull/81
name: v0.20.1

body: * Fix git URL regex issue with optional user name: https://github.com/jingweno/gh/pull/80
name: v0.20.0

body: * Fix bug in parsing user and branch from pull request url
name: v0.19.1

body:
* Implement `gh apply`
* Fix bug in remote url matching
* Implement `gh push`
name: v0.17.0

body: * Fix git head not working for all git versions
name: v0.13.1

body: * Extract GitHub API related code to [`octokat`](https://github.com/jingweno/octokat)
name: v0.5.2

body:
* Implement `gh checkout`
* Rename `gh pull` to `gh pr`
name: v0.8.0

body:
* Implement `gh clone`
* Fix various bugs in `gh remote`
* Rename `gh pr` `gh pull-request` to avoid potential alias collision
* Rename `gh ci` `gh ci-status` to avoid potential alias collision
name: v0.10.0
